@startuml
skinparam backgroundColor #ECEFF1
skinparam classBackgroundColor #FFFFFF
skinparam classBorderColor #455A64
[*] --> Archived
Archived --> Delivered : review
Delivered --> Rejected : cancel
Rejected --> Cancelled : reject
Cancelled --> Active : update
Cancelled : entry / log cart
Active --> Created : submit
Created --> Active : revert
Created --> [*]
@enduml